 why we get on well together my coat and i it has acquired all my folds it does not bind me anywhere it is moulded on my deformities it falls in with all my movements i am only conscious of it because it keeps me warm 
 old coats are just like old friends 
 true ejaculated joly striking into the dialogue an old goat is an old abi ami friend 
